thread.title: Martin Lewis
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Martin Lewis

author: Martin Lewis
title: Martin Lewis
text: Although the car was a little older it was great we drove over 600 miles and was very comfortable, great price and the people were happy to pick up from the airport and they drove us back to the airport. Not a flashing dwelling but great service and the people were genuine would go there again.
